## Usage with Earmark

If following  lines are

    ... normal markdown
    $$ ruby 10 100 4
    $$ elixir 40 800 12
    ... still more normal markdown

read into `lines`


    Earmark.as_html(lines, Earmark.Plugin.define(EarmarkTagCloud))

Please see [Earmark](https://github.com/pragdave/earmark)  for more details of how to use plugins

